===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# a [[muscular]] [[organ]] that [[pump]]s [[blood]] through the [[body]].
# emotions or kindness in general (but like above, people only have one heart).
#: ''In Sylvester Stallone's famous movie Lock Up, Frank Leone has a '''heart''' of gold.''
# a shape or symbol approximately in the shape of a heart (♥).
# a playing card of the suit [[hearts]] featuring one or more heart-shaped symbols.
# the centre or core.

